WEBVTT

00:00:00.855 --> 00:00:04.966
KASETA MISPAR ARBA. HANITSOLA NINA Zlatkin.

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:07.819
NINA, nokh di shpitol,

00:00:08.280 --> 00:00:11.818
 dertseylt undz vos iz p- vos hot pasirt.

00:00:11.723 --> 00:00:14.300
nokhn shpitol hobn zey mir av-

00:00:14.300 --> 00:00:16.324
avekgefirt in aza,

00:00:16.667 --> 00:00:21.099
in aza oysbeserungs-hoyz, ikh zol zikh farrikhtn a bi-...

00:00:21.291 --> 00:00:23.996
ober mir iz dortn geven nit gut,

00:00:23.996 --> 00:00:28.490
bin ikh in mitn nakht antlofn fun dortn tsu di khaverte.

00:00:29.020 --> 00:00:31.832
hob ikh gelebt tsuzamen mit di khaverte

00:00:32.682 --> 00:00:34.785
un, dortn hobn mir zikh...

00:00:33.660 --> 00:00:36.708
mit Sheyne? Sheyne un d- ir shvester?

00:00:35.050 --> 00:00:38.024
⟨z-⟩ Sheyne, ya, ya, un shvester MINA.

00:00:38.031 --> 00:00:39.797
zi lebt in KHAYFA.

00:00:39.837 --> 00:00:43.982
zi iz a y- y- a, geven nokh a yunge meydlke, di Sheyne,

00:00:44.022 --> 00:00:47.070
ober di Sheyne iz vi ikh in eyn elter.

00:00:47.886 --> 00:00:51.896
hobn mir, gelebt dortn in, LAUENBURG.

00:00:52.425 --> 00:00:55.932
un in LAUENBURG hob ikh zikh bakant dortn mi-

00:00:55.932 --> 00:00:59.895
mit, a direktor fun turme, ikh hob far ir geneyt.

00:01:00.272 --> 00:01:03.118
un der altitshker iz geven bay undz.

00:01:03.242 --> 00:01:06.358
mir flegn moyre hobn aroystsugeyn oyfn gas,

00:01:06.938 --> 00:01:10.746
fleg der altitshker ongegenen di VOENNe mentshn,

00:01:11.393 --> 00:01:13.780
di,... un er flegt

00:01:13.857 --> 00:01:16.112
undz derkazhenen esn,

00:01:16.320 --> 00:01:18.558
vayle m'hot nit gekent aroysgeyn.

00:01:18.801 --> 00:01:23.440
ir veyst dokh, ⟨iz⟩ dortn di daytshn, zey flegn fargevaldikn... di rusishe.

00:01:23.003 --> 00:01:25.444
di rusishe, nisht keyn daytshn?

00:01:23.820 --> 00:01:27.843
ya, di rusishe shoyn. neyn, di rusishe iz shoyn geven.

00:01:27.843 --> 00:01:32.570
azoy arum az mir hobn dortn moy- moy- m'hot moyre gehat,

00:01:32.757 --> 00:01:34.897
heyst dos, aroystsugeyn.

00:01:34.897 --> 00:01:38.505
flegt er undz derkazhenen tsu es- esn.

00:01:39.085 --> 00:01:45.139
un az me fleg darfn geyn tsu di khaverte, gedenk ikh, flegt men zikh onton vi an altitshke mit a shtekn,

00:01:45.139 --> 00:01:48.224
un mir flegn avekgeyn in shpitol.

00:01:48.298 --> 00:01:51.262
dernokh, az m'iz shoyn beser gevorn,

00:01:51.302 --> 00:01:55.300
hobn mir zikh a bisl tsayt dortn geven in LAUENBURG.

00:01:56.668 --> 00:02:01.606
nu, m- m- un, mir hobn nit gevust vayter vos iz der goyrl.

00:02:02.085 --> 00:02:07.158
iz men gekumen fun di rusn un zey hobn gezogn az me darf traybn ki tsu fus.

00:02:07.958 --> 00:02:11.650
tsu fus zoln mir geyn un traybn di ki oyf Rusland.

00:02:12.970 --> 00:02:15.616
hobn mir, mir ⟨hobn⟩ zikh antzagt.

00:02:15.616 --> 00:02:19.910
mir hobn zikh bahaltn vi, vayle gey trayb tsu fus di fi.

00:02:19.618 --> 00:02:22.497
ir hot getrofn nokh yidishe mentshn?

00:02:21.964 --> 00:02:27.630
ya! bafrayte fun lager, fun lager geven in LAUENBURG, iz geven a sakh.

00:02:27.043 --> 00:02:27.982
a sakh?

00:02:28.208 --> 00:02:29.164
a sakh.

00:02:29.237 --> 00:02:33.112
ober andere zaynen glaykh avek in Poyln, andere...

00:02:33.135 --> 00:02:36.926
du host shoyn gehert, ETWAS fun dayn man?

00:02:33.590 --> 00:02:35.180
ikh veys, mir zaynen...

00:02:37.624 --> 00:02:41.750
fun mayn... vu hob ikh gehert fun mayn man? ikh'l derts-... keyn zakh nit.

00:02:39.160 --> 00:02:40.622
nokh nisht gehert?

00:02:42.730 --> 00:02:49.045
d- meyle, mir UNK dortn geven a p-, a bisl tsayt in LAUENBURG,

00:02:49.045 --> 00:02:51.456
un dernokh iz gekumen

00:02:51.900 --> 00:02:54.020
a rusisher kapitan,

00:02:55.326 --> 00:02:58.745
a kapi- an ofitser a groyser, a rusisher,

00:02:58.971 --> 00:03:03.521
un er hot undz gehaltn a rede, vayle mir hobn gehert dortn tsu a punkt.

00:03:04.759 --> 00:03:07.841
repatryantn heyst dos, hobn mir zikh gerufn.

00:03:08.320 --> 00:03:10.330
un er hot gezogt,

00:03:10.330 --> 00:03:13.540
"ir, dervayle aheym vet nit forn,

00:03:13.540 --> 00:03:17.781
vayle mir darfn nit brengen keyn rusishe birger fun Rusland,

00:03:18.090 --> 00:03:21.324
nor UNK vi ir zayt do repatryantn,

00:03:22.815 --> 00:03:25.745
iz nemen mir, nem ikh aykh oyf arbet."

00:03:26.781 --> 00:03:31.584
dos heyst, in a VOENNem, azoy vi do a, a kibuts,

00:03:32.130 --> 00:03:34.554
dos ⟨hey-⟩ a VOENNer SOVKHOZ.

00:03:34.797 --> 00:03:37.305
dos hot gehert nor tsu di,

00:03:37.378 --> 00:03:39.852
f- tsu zeyere, tsu di melukhishe.

00:03:41.040 --> 00:03:46.349
un er hot undz gebrakht tsu zikh in, in, in SOVKHOZ,

00:03:46.727 --> 00:03:50.248
un er fregt, "vos vilt ir do ton?"

00:03:50.288 --> 00:03:52.931
un mir zaynen geven azoy ayngeshrokn.

00:03:53.258 --> 00:03:56.137
zogn mir, "keyn ki kenen mir nit traybn!"

00:03:56.370 --> 00:03:59.951
 zogt er, "bay mir vet ir nit traybn keyn ki,

00:04:00.042 --> 00:04:03.968
un ir vet, do iz a khazyaystve," heyst dos, a...

00:04:04.024 --> 00:04:05.936
nu, vi,

00:04:05.936 --> 00:04:10.143
dortn iz gevezn ki mit ferd mit, mit khazeyrim

00:04:10.150 --> 00:04:11.730
in di hunderter.

00:04:12.462 --> 00:04:15.460
"un ver ken fun aykh reydn rusish?"

00:04:16.156 --> 00:04:20.301
un ikh hob gekent reydn rusish, mayne khaverte nit.

00:04:21.168 --> 00:04:27.373
un mir zaynen gekumen dortn tsu forn... heyst dos, er hot undz genumen in SOVKHOZ...

00:04:28.240 --> 00:04:33.684
un mir hot men glaykh gegebn a shtele, v⟨os⟩ ikh bin geven a onfirerke fun fir derfer.

00:04:34.450 --> 00:04:37.701
bay mir zaynen gezesn daytshkes PKIDOT

00:04:37.943 --> 00:04:39.557
un zey hobn gearbet,

00:04:39.765 --> 00:04:42.577
un ikh hob opgenumen fun zey di OTCHЁTn.

00:04:43.174 --> 00:04:47.116
un ikh hob gedarft far plenikes... geven daytshishe...

00:04:47.258 --> 00:04:49.412
hob ikh zey gedarft gebn esn.

00:04:50.869 --> 00:04:54.215
dernokh flegn vifl mol tsu mir kumen daytshkes,

00:04:54.215 --> 00:04:56.720
hob ikh zey aropgetribn fun di trep.

00:04:56.995 --> 00:04:58.963
kh'hob nit gekent kukn,

00:04:59.037 --> 00:05:02.490
vayle az ikh ⟨b-⟩ bay undz hot men tsugenumen di kinder.

00:05:02.490 --> 00:05:04.950
zey flegn kumen mit di kinder,

00:05:04.950 --> 00:05:08.900
bin ikh geven azoy BROGEZ az vifl mol fleg ikh nit kenen reydn.

00:05:08.900 --> 00:05:12.500
ober ikh hob gemuzt dortn mitn goyrl zikh,...

00:05:12.500 --> 00:05:14.303
vayle ikh hob gearbet.

00:05:15.203 --> 00:05:18.960
un ikh, m- m- ikh hob, mir hobn gearbet tsevishn di rusn.

00:05:18.915 --> 00:05:21.035
velekhe tsayt iz dos gevezn?

00:05:19.039 --> 00:05:20.039
un...

00:05:21.328 --> 00:05:24.461
velkhe tsayt? dos iz geven, in fir,

00:05:24.552 --> 00:05:28.376
in onfang finf un fertsikstn yor, beshas m'hot undz bafrayt.

00:05:29.732 --> 00:05:35.390
un dortn, fun dortn hobn mir gevelt forn aheym, ober mir hobn nit UNK,

00:05:35.390 --> 00:05:39.100
mir hobn nit gevust vu tsu forn, ven tsu forn, ver es le-...

00:05:39.182 --> 00:05:41.830
ober mir zaynen nokh nit geforn.

00:05:41.830 --> 00:05:44.590
un dortn zaynen mir geven,

00:05:44.590 --> 00:05:48.001
hobn mir zikh shoyn farrikht un mir hobn shoyn gegesn,

00:05:48.210 --> 00:05:51.070
un mir hobn gehat fun altsding.

00:05:51.070 --> 00:05:55.240
un ikh bin geven a baleboste; mir flegn avekfirn in shtot,

00:05:55.240 --> 00:05:59.880
 a khazerl, un farkoyfn bishtike un hobn gelt

00:05:59.880 --> 00:06:01.588
oyf fotografyes.

00:06:01.588 --> 00:06:04.083
un dortn iz shoyn undz geven gut.

00:06:04.309 --> 00:06:08.043
ober aheymforn nit. hobn mir genumen shraybn briv.

00:06:08.043 --> 00:06:09.731
di khaverte's man

00:06:09.731 --> 00:06:13.314
iz oykh geven mit mayn man tsuzamen in DACHAU.

00:06:13.950 --> 00:06:18.253
hot men gezogt az DACHAU hot men alemen oysgeshosn mit al⟨ts⟩.

00:06:18.253 --> 00:06:21.481
ober azoy vi ikh hob in ŠIAULIAI,

00:06:21.775 --> 00:06:26.090
 hob ikh gearbet dan in geto, hot men mir aroysgelozn

00:06:26.090 --> 00:06:26.980
bay dem,

00:06:28.086 --> 00:06:30.847
 balebos fun ban, vu ikh hob gearbet,

00:06:31.242 --> 00:06:34.240
hob ikh on-, ongeshribn a briv.

00:06:35.070 --> 00:06:38.575
 hob ikh geshribn tsu di baleboste:

00:06:39.308 --> 00:06:41.732
"velkhn yidn du vest trefn,

00:06:42.430 --> 00:06:44.752
zolstu opgebn dem briv."

00:06:47.037 --> 00:06:50.507
mayn man hot zikh bafrayt fun DACHAU

00:06:52.302 --> 00:06:54.780
un... i- in finf un fertsik...

00:06:54.934 --> 00:06:58.893
un azoy vi mir hobn opgeredt, er hot dokh gekent forn in oysland,

00:06:58.933 --> 00:07:02.521
in Amerike; mir zaynen geven poylishe birger.

00:07:02.697 --> 00:07:05.779
iz er gelofn mir zukhn in Lite,

00:07:06.038 --> 00:07:08.934
un er iz gekumen in di shtot ŠIAULIAI.

00:07:09.750 --> 00:07:13.912
er iz gekumen, er mit dem, mit mayn khaverte's kha-, man,

00:07:14.273 --> 00:07:16.865
gekumen in shtot ŠIAULIAI: vu?

00:07:17.007 --> 00:07:19.836
nit me veys fun mir, nit me veys.

00:07:19.892 --> 00:07:23.295
efsher bin ikh geharget gevorn, efsher vos.

00:07:23.503 --> 00:07:27.277
⟨i-⟩ a yor tsayt hot er nit gevust k- hot nit gevust.

00:07:27.790 --> 00:07:30.585
ober abi kh'hob shoyn geshribn dem briv,

00:07:30.709 --> 00:07:34.162
iz punkt arayngefaln tsu a yidn in di hent,

00:07:34.371 --> 00:07:37.099
un mayn man hot gekrogn dem briv.

00:07:37.425 --> 00:07:40.679
hob ikh zikh genumen mit mayn man shraybn.

00:07:40.679 --> 00:07:46.770
ober mir zaynen geven azoy farshpart bay di VOENNe, bay di rusn,

00:07:46.770 --> 00:07:49.590
az mir hobn nokh nit gekent forn aheym.

00:07:49.930 --> 00:07:53.050
zey hobn undz nit opgelozn, vayle mir hobn gehat

00:07:53.050 --> 00:07:55.750
arbet arum dortn.

00:07:55.750 --> 00:07:58.850
zey hobn farnumen a sakh ki mit ferd mit,

00:07:58.850 --> 00:08:02.347
mit, mit, mit, mit, mit ⟨vo- v-⟩ mit khazeyrim;

00:08:02.347 --> 00:08:04.335
dos iz alts fun di daytshn.

00:08:04.560 --> 00:08:08.789
iz hobn mir dos gedarft alts hitn biz vanet m'vet ariberfirn.

00:08:09.505 --> 00:08:11.962
 hot men undz nit opgelozn.

00:08:12.103 --> 00:08:17.952
un azoy zaynen mir geven zeyer a sakh tsayt. ikh hob zikh oyfgeshribn mit mayn man.

00:08:19.073 --> 00:08:23.083
un, ikh hob zikh dervust az er lebt shoyn,

00:08:23.089 --> 00:08:25.667
vayle eyne, mir zaynen geforn,

00:08:25.667 --> 00:08:29.464
mir zaynen geforn... dortn iz geven, lebn LAUENBURG,

00:08:29.464 --> 00:08:32.330
vu mir z- iz geven a shtot, nokh eyne.

00:08:32.330 --> 00:08:35.126
iz dortn hot gearbet undzere a khaverte.

00:08:35.126 --> 00:08:37.775
zi iz tsuzamen bafrayt gevorn,

00:08:37.775 --> 00:08:40.396
un zi iz geven a tson-doktershe.

00:08:40.774 --> 00:08:43.805
zaynen mir shoyn gekumen tsu ir tsu gest,

00:08:44.217 --> 00:08:47.670
un oyf ir kabinet iz geven ⟨a-⟩ ongeshribn

00:08:47.912 --> 00:08:50.590
az "far yidn, der arayngang

00:08:50.590 --> 00:08:51.872
iz farbotn."

00:08:52.114 --> 00:08:55.348
heyst dos, der kabinet iz geven irer. "far yidn,

00:08:55.422 --> 00:09:00.056
arayngang farbotn." ober m'hot bafrayt, hot zi gehat dem kabinet.

00:09:00.467 --> 00:09:03.802
un tsu ir zaynen gekumen tsvey bakante,

00:09:04.062 --> 00:09:07.307
vos zey zaynen bafrayt gevorn fun DACHAU,

00:09:07.307 --> 00:09:10.941
un zey hobn gezogt az mayn man mit mayn khaverte's man lebn.

00:09:11.858 --> 00:09:15.463
un ikh hob genumen shraybn briv un ikh hob zikh oyfgeshribn.

00:09:15.807 --> 00:09:18.011
hob ikh gezogt tsu mayn man,

00:09:19.300 --> 00:09:22.433
"kum tsu forn tsurik in oysland."

00:09:23.063 --> 00:09:26.297
hot mayn man gezogt, "neyn." s'iz im geven gut.

00:09:26.337 --> 00:09:29.486
er iz glaykh arayn in di zelbe fabrik arbetn,

00:09:29.661 --> 00:09:32.250
un er hot fardint a sakh gelt,

00:09:32.901 --> 00:09:36.877
un er hot gezogt, "ikh vil nit forn. ikh vil, zolst kumen aher."

00:09:37.812 --> 00:09:41.550
meyle, mir zaynen geven dortn zeyer a sakh tsayt.

00:09:41.550 --> 00:09:45.383
dernokh hob ikh dortn bakant eynem a yidishn mayor.

00:09:46.637 --> 00:09:51.238
di VETERINARNe doktoyrim zaynen geven mayorn ale.

00:09:51.480 --> 00:09:54.933
dos iz groyse tshinen, a mayor. ir veyst vi...?

00:09:54.147 --> 00:09:55.187
yo, yo.

00:09:55.834 --> 00:09:58.545
hob ikh bakant a yidishn mayor.

00:09:58.838 --> 00:10:01.262
kh'hob im dertseylt mayn lage,

00:10:01.673 --> 00:10:04.920
azoy vi ikh hob zikh b- mayn m-

00:10:04.920 --> 00:10:06.960
 ikh vil forn aheym.

00:10:06.960 --> 00:10:08.540
kh'hob im nit gezogt

00:10:08.540 --> 00:10:13.010
"tsu mayn man" tsi vos. kh'hob gezogt, "ikh vil zen tsi mayn man lebt."

00:10:13.283 --> 00:10:14.820
dem mayor.

00:10:14.820 --> 00:10:21.039
vayle er UNK... ikh bin im zeyer gefeln gevorn, a yidisher mayor, un er hot farlorn zayn familye.

00:10:21.923 --> 00:10:24.100
hot er mir ge- dos,

00:10:24.100 --> 00:10:26.020
er hot dos mir gemakht,

00:10:26.020 --> 00:10:28.110
az ikh zol kenen forn aheym,

00:10:29.095 --> 00:10:32.930
un dernokh a protektsye far di khaverte.

00:10:32.930 --> 00:10:35.788
nor far mir hot er gemakht frier.

00:10:36.638 --> 00:10:41.796
un, ⟨i- un, n-⟩ ober ikh bin a tsayt dortn geven.

00:10:42.342 --> 00:10:45.289
zog ikh, "ikh'l kumen, ikh'l kumen in shtub,

00:10:45.835 --> 00:10:47.162
un ikh'l zen:

00:10:47.168 --> 00:10:52.446
oybe mayn man lebt nit, vel ikh zikh mit dir oyfshraybn. ikh zog dir...

00:10:52.446 --> 00:10:55.146
nor tomer lebt mayn man,

00:10:55.146 --> 00:10:59.716
iz vel ikh blaybn mit mayn man, vayl ikh hob tsu mayn man gornit."

00:11:00.077 --> 00:11:03.170
meyle, er hot mir ale papirn gemakht,

00:11:03.486 --> 00:11:05.808
un ikh bin gekumen tsu forn

00:11:06.591 --> 00:11:09.330
tsu mayn man in ŠIAULIAI,

00:11:09.330 --> 00:11:10.958
un mayn khaverte

00:11:10.958 --> 00:11:13.329
iz gekumen in a vokh arum.

00:11:13.329 --> 00:11:16.524
azoy zaynen mir fun dortn bafrayt gevorn.

00:11:18.201 --> 00:11:19.747
ven iz dos geven?

00:11:19.956 --> 00:11:22.590
dos iz geven shoyn zeks un fertsik.

00:11:23.533 --> 00:11:26.142
ya. bistu gekumen in ŠIAULIAI...

00:11:24.210 --> 00:11:26.410
bin ikh gekumen in ŠIAULIAI,

00:11:26.410 --> 00:11:28.438
un dan hobn mir oyfgeshtelt,

00:11:28.579 --> 00:11:31.121
dan hobn mir oyfgeshtelt di matseyve.

00:11:32.130 --> 00:11:34.130
far d-..., eyn minut.

00:11:34.070 --> 00:11:35.040
ha?

00:11:34.130 --> 00:11:37.635
, bald vestu vizn di bi- bilder.

00:11:36.325 --> 00:11:39.052
dan hobn mir oyfge⟨tsel⟩t di matseyve

00:11:39.140 --> 00:11:40.920
yo. far,

00:11:39.620 --> 00:11:41.340
fun mayn tokhter.

00:11:40.920 --> 00:11:43.940
far,...

00:11:42.923 --> 00:11:46.960
shoyn bafrayt, ikh bin shoyn gekumen tsu mayn man. er hot fardint...

00:11:45.133 --> 00:11:48.687
far dos meydele vos zi iz geshtorbn in disenterye?

00:11:48.407 --> 00:11:52.501
y- di meydele vos iz geshtorbn; zi iz gelegn dokh in geto.

00:11:50.550 --> 00:11:51.610
un...

00:11:51.816 --> 00:11:54.300
yo. hot men gemakht a matseyve.

00:11:53.554 --> 00:11:56.660
hobn mir oyfgemakht a sheyne matseyve, ot.

00:11:55.815 --> 00:11:58.003
host... un do- UNK

00:11:56.912 --> 00:12:02.272
un oyfgeshribn az di, fun di daytshishe hent vi zi iz ⟨oyf⟩gekumen.

00:12:02.481 --> 00:12:07.370
un ikh hob, un mir, ikh hob dortn nit gevelt mer zayn,

00:12:07.088 --> 00:12:09.309
host ge- geforn ⟨f-⟩...?

00:12:08.252 --> 00:12:09.528
in ŠIAULIAI.

00:12:09.687 --> 00:12:12.921
un in Vilne, vu ikh hob geborn gevorn,

00:12:12.943 --> 00:12:15.181
hob ikh oykh nit gevelt kumen;

00:12:15.373 --> 00:12:18.742
ikh hob dortn ⟨a-⟩ farlorn azoy fil mishpokhe.

00:12:18.917 --> 00:12:21.560
zaynen mir aroysgeforn in KAUNAS.

00:12:21.921 --> 00:12:26.170
BEFORE THAT, bef-, befor aroysforn keyn KAUNAS,

00:12:26.170 --> 00:12:29.780
zent ir, hot ir gezukht dos meydele vos zi iz ge-

00:12:29.150 --> 00:12:32.259
a, ya. ikh hob gezukht di kleyninke.

00:12:29.780 --> 00:12:31.719
nokhn geburt...? yo.

00:12:31.843 --> 00:12:33.187
di kleyninke.

00:12:32.805 --> 00:12:35.880
vayzt zikh aroys, eyns fun di beyde, der, d-

00:12:35.880 --> 00:12:37.845
der kinder-heym iz nit geven:

00:12:38.020 --> 00:12:41.380
oder der kinder-heym hot men vu ibergefirt,

00:12:41.380 --> 00:12:45.911
"oder," zey zogn, "ken zayn az di kinder hot men i- ergets vu adoptirt."

00:12:46.491 --> 00:12:47.413
shoyn.

00:12:47.824 --> 00:12:50.096
kh'hob keyn eyn simen nit gehat,

00:12:50.490 --> 00:12:54.621
az m'hot ir ongeton a tseylem, un ikh hob nit gemakht, m'hot mir avekgefirt,

00:12:54.621 --> 00:12:58.179
azoy krank; ikh hob nit gevust az m'vet ir azoy gikh tsunemen.

00:12:58.557 --> 00:13:01.588
iz f- fun di kind iz nit geven keyn...

00:13:02.303 --> 00:13:06.046
bin ikh gekumen un ikh hob gevelt farshvangern;

00:13:06.046 --> 00:13:11.207
ikh bin nokh geven a yunge. kh'hob nit gekent. ikh bin geven zeyer krank.

00:13:11.365 --> 00:13:15.240
un ikh hob zikh geheylt bay di greste profesorn.

00:13:15.786 --> 00:13:18.784
s'iz geven profesor Levitan

00:13:19.144 --> 00:13:21.855
in Kov- in Kovne... in Vilne,

00:13:22.468 --> 00:13:26.461
vos er hot geleygt far mir... ikh hob im zeyer a sakh batsolt...

00:13:26.839 --> 00:13:31.305
er hot zikh ge- ge- ge- far mir zeyer gestaret, ikh zol,

00:13:31.395 --> 00:13:35.000
ikh zol kenen krign, ikh zol kenen sh- farshvangern,

00:13:35.513 --> 00:13:40.367
ober s'hot gedoyert fun zeks un fertsik bizn fuftsikstn yor.

00:13:40.710 --> 00:13:43.741
un ikh bin geforn oyf ale kurortn.

00:13:44.338 --> 00:13:46.110
un ikh hob farshvangert.

00:13:45.739 --> 00:13:47.235
in fuftsikstn?

00:13:46.363 --> 00:13:50.097
ikh bin geven in ĶEMERI in Letland oyf a kurort,

00:13:50.097 --> 00:13:53.500
un dortn kumendik hob ikh shoyn farshvangert.

00:13:53.974 --> 00:13:55.908
in velekhe yor iz dos geven?

00:13:54.057 --> 00:13:55.110
un az i-...

00:13:55.763 --> 00:13:59.480
dos iz geven, ikh hob f- ikh hob ir gehat in fuftsikstn yor.

00:13:59.205 --> 00:14:00.042
ya.

00:13:59.480 --> 00:14:01.690
dos iz geven nayn un fertsik.

00:14:00.741 --> 00:14:01.578
ya.

00:14:03.576 --> 00:14:10.200
nu, ikh bin geven, ikh hob di bilder, vos ikh bin geven oyf di kurortn mit umetum, ikh hob zikh geLECHet.

00:14:06.495 --> 00:14:07.282
ya.

00:14:10.200 --> 00:14:13.892
dernokh, az ikh bin arayngegangen in shpitol

00:14:13.892 --> 00:14:17.137
tsu hobn di, di, di tokhter mayne,

00:14:17.953 --> 00:14:21.690
vayzt zikh aroys az zi iz gelegn bay mir in der kver.

00:14:21.690 --> 00:14:25.889
nayn monat bin ikh oysgelegn oyf a bet. kh'hob geblutikt

00:14:25.889 --> 00:14:28.860
un kh'hob nit gekent hobn di kind.

00:14:28.860 --> 00:14:32.480
m'hot mir gehit un m'hot mir avekgefirt tsum profesor,

00:14:32.480 --> 00:14:35.160
hot er ongezogt, "me darf ir hitn,

00:14:35.160 --> 00:14:37.407
vayle zi iz a gelitene mame

00:14:37.407 --> 00:14:41.235
un zi hot tsvey kinder farlorn un zi ken nit farshvangern."

00:14:43.080 --> 00:14:47.844
un m⟨'ho⟩t dos o, un, un m'hot mir zeyer gehit dortn in,

00:14:47.844 --> 00:14:49.605
in shpitol in Vilne.

00:14:49.341 --> 00:14:50.145
yo.

00:14:50.016 --> 00:14:52.659
hot men mir avekgefirt in shpitol,

00:14:52.783 --> 00:14:56.787
un, vayle zi iz gelegn i- bay mir in der kver.

00:14:56.787 --> 00:14:59.324
un ikh hob ir geborn.

00:15:00.208 --> 00:15:02.244
ikh hob ir geborn.

00:15:02.706 --> 00:15:04.927
un vi ikh hob ir ertsoygn,

00:15:05.710 --> 00:15:10.642
un s'iz far ir keyn zakh tsu ta-... in tsvey yor arum hob ikh farshvangert aleyn

00:15:10.642 --> 00:15:12.554
mit di tsveyte tokhter.

00:15:12.763 --> 00:15:15.727
mit mi- mit ir iz shoyn mir geven laykhter.

00:15:16.037 --> 00:15:17.718
dos iz in yor,

00:15:18.113 --> 00:15:22.967
 eyn un fuftsik in detsember, dos iz onfang tsvey un fuftsikstn yor,

00:15:23.142 --> 00:15:25.093
hob ikh gehat di tsveyte.

00:15:25.842 --> 00:15:28.772
nu, un ikh hob zikh gelebt shoyn gut.

00:15:28.913 --> 00:15:31.337
in nayn un fuftsikstn yor

00:15:31.613 --> 00:15:33.564
zaynen mir gekumen do.

00:15:33.672 --> 00:15:35.050
in velekhe yor?

00:15:35.157 --> 00:15:37.050
in nayn un fuftsik.

00:15:35.967 --> 00:15:37.547
nayn un fuftsik, yo.

00:15:37.249 --> 00:15:42.221
fun zeks un fertsik bi- ⟨hobn mir,⟩ di gantse tsayt hobn mir gelebt in KAUNAS.

00:15:41.991 --> 00:15:42.693
ya.

00:15:43.257 --> 00:15:47.453
nayn un fertsikstn yor... ikh hob zeyer nit gevelt forn,

00:15:47.644 --> 00:15:50.770
vayle mir hobn zeyer gut gelebt dortn,

00:15:50.770 --> 00:15:53.510
mit a OTO, mit alts,

00:15:53.510 --> 00:15:58.770
ober der lebn iz geven rizikalish, vayle m'hot nit getort haltn keyn eygene gesheftn.

00:15:58.770 --> 00:16:01.150
m'hot keyn zakh nit getort haltn.

00:16:01.161 --> 00:16:04.479
nor alts iz geven, s'iz geven Rusland.

00:16:05.937 --> 00:16:09.053
iz, mayn man hot gezogt

00:16:09.531 --> 00:16:13.254
az mir muzn fun danet avekgeyn tsulib di kinder,

00:16:13.378 --> 00:16:16.595
vayle zey zoln nit khasene hobn mit keyn goyim.

00:16:17.800 --> 00:16:21.280
un mir zaynen ge- mir zaynen aroysgeforn

00:16:21.280 --> 00:16:25.371
nit als litvishe, nor m'hot aroys- geven a gezets

00:16:25.714 --> 00:16:28.720
az di poylishe birger lozt men aroys.

00:16:29.562 --> 00:16:33.302
nor eyn zakh vil ikh dermonen: beshas ikh bin nokh geven in,

00:16:33.443 --> 00:16:35.450
dortn bay di rusn

00:16:35.450 --> 00:16:39.370
un mayn man iz geven do, flegt men im ale tog rufn:

00:16:39.370 --> 00:16:42.000
"far vos gefint zikh dayn vayb in,

00:16:42.000 --> 00:16:45.868
far vo- far vos gefint zikh nokh dayn vayb oyf di daytshishe gebitn?"

00:16:45.868 --> 00:16:48.160
zogt er az me lozt ir nit op.

00:16:48.160 --> 00:16:50.331
ale tog flegt men im rufn,

00:16:50.331 --> 00:16:52.033
far vos ikh bin nito.

00:16:52.545 --> 00:16:58.912
nu, un dernokh, az mir hobn gele- in nayn un fuftsikstn yor, poylishe birger hot men aroysgelozn,

00:16:58.912 --> 00:17:02.120
zaynen mir geku- aroysgeforn in Lodzh.

00:17:02.120 --> 00:17:06.984
m'hot undz gebrakht oykh mit a transport v- vi rep⟨r⟩atryantn.

00:17:07.445 --> 00:17:11.539
ober mir hobn gehat gelt, hobn mir genumen a dire in Lodzh,

00:17:11.766 --> 00:17:14.270
un dortn hobn mir gelebt,

00:17:14.500 --> 00:17:16.266
 tsvey yor,

00:17:16.795 --> 00:17:18.797
fun zibn un fuftsik

00:17:19.309 --> 00:17:22.495
biz nayn un fuftsik, in Lodzh. m'hot undz nit aro-...

00:17:21.300 --> 00:17:22.138
yo.

00:17:22.495 --> 00:17:26.929
s'iz geven a gezets ⟨az in⟩ IZRAIL' iz shoyn geve- iz geven farbotn tsu forn.

00:17:26.970 --> 00:17:30.069
un mir hobn avekgegebn zeyer a sakh

00:17:30.362 --> 00:17:33.697
PO BLATU, me zol undz aroyslozn.

00:17:34.227 --> 00:17:39.655
un in nayn un fuftsikstn yor zaynen mir aroysgeforn, gekumen in ARETS.

00:17:39.728 --> 00:17:45.662
mir zaynen gekumen in Poyln, iz eyne geven bay mir finf yor un eyne zibn yor.

00:17:46.933 --> 00:17:48.680
nu, in Poyln.

00:17:48.216 --> 00:17:49.037
yo.

00:17:48.773 --> 00:17:51.095
un mir zaynen gekumen do, iz shoyn

00:17:51.169 --> 00:17:55.120
eyne geven zibn, un eyne ⟨iz⟩ geven nayn.

00:17:52.975 --> 00:17:54.302
vi,...

00:17:54.645 --> 00:17:56.124
di meydelekh?

00:17:55.911 --> 00:17:58.908
un ikh hob gehat zeyer a shvern, ⟨s'iz⟩ shver do,

00:17:59.117 --> 00:18:01.406
eyder m'hot zikh ayngeordnt.

00:18:00.265 --> 00:18:03.195
vu zent ir gekOmen? UNK, vu...

00:18:02.155 --> 00:18:07.020
mir zaynen do gekumen, iz, UNK undz ibergenumen a korev.

00:18:06.880 --> 00:18:09.737
in velekhn pla- plats hot ir gevoynt?

00:18:08.880 --> 00:18:09.840
ha?

00:18:09.737 --> 00:18:12.206
in velekhn plats hot ir gevoynt do?

00:18:11.706 --> 00:18:16.260
ikh hob gevoyn- frier hot undz ibergenumen in Tel-Aviv a korev. ⟨mir hobn⟩...

00:18:16.260 --> 00:18:19.100
un er hot undz gemakht a protektsye,

00:18:19.100 --> 00:18:22.618
un mir hobn gekrogn in KFAR SAVA a sheyne dire.

00:18:23.890 --> 00:18:31.343
ober in KFAR SAVA hob ikh, hobn mir nit gevelt zayn, vayle mir hobn gedarft arbetn, un ikh hob oykh gevelt arbetn.

00:18:31.618 --> 00:18:36.354
hobn mir ge-... un mayn man hot glaykh gekrogn dernokh arbet

00:18:36.445 --> 00:18:39.662
in a groyse fabrik, ober azoy vi er iz geven

00:18:39.972 --> 00:18:42.851
a groyser spetsyalist, m'hot im gedarft,

00:18:43.093 --> 00:18:47.069
hot men gemakht a protektsye un m'hot undz ibergefirt in BAT YAM.

00:18:47.110 --> 00:18:50.124
un in BAT YAM fleg ikh oykh geyn arbetn.

00:18:50.670 --> 00:18:53.240
di kinder flegn blaybn in shtub.

00:18:52.662 --> 00:18:54.141
vu hostu gearbet?

00:18:55.092 --> 00:18:57.358
mayn man iz geven a modelyor

00:18:57.133 --> 00:18:58.021
yo.

00:18:57.358 --> 00:19:00.450
un er flegt makhn DUGMAOT oyf di shikh.

00:19:00.450 --> 00:19:02.223
fleg ikh avektrogn,

00:19:02.247 --> 00:19:03.625
hob ikh gezen

00:19:03.816 --> 00:19:09.007
az dortn zitsn di vos endikn aroys di shikh, FINISHER, un zey fardinen gut.

00:19:09.013 --> 00:19:14.407
iz vos hob ikh geton? hob ikh UNK oysgelernt dem fakh, kh'hob gehat protektsye, un ikh hob gearbet.

00:19:14.413 --> 00:19:15.760
kh'hob geholfn,

00:19:15.760 --> 00:19:19.190
vayle kh'hob gevelt, di kinder zoln shpiln akordyon,

00:19:19.190 --> 00:19:21.292
zoln lernen in TIKHON,

00:19:21.315 --> 00:19:23.840
zoln geyn sheyn ongeton.

00:19:24.960 --> 00:19:29.594
 hob ikh ge- hob ikh gedarft helfn arbetn. mir hobn gehat a ⟨MISHKANTA⟩.

00:19:29.820 --> 00:19:32.850
kh'hob itster oykh di dire in BAT YAM;

00:19:32.850 --> 00:19:37.340
ikh hob ir d- itster hob ikh arayngelozn in di dire mayn eynikl,

00:19:37.988 --> 00:19:40.969
vayle, vos di tokhter iz geshtorbn.

00:19:41.447 --> 00:19:43.090
dertseyl vos...

00:19:41.850 --> 00:19:43.651
vayle der eynikl

00:19:44.340 --> 00:19:46.180
iz zeks un...

00:19:44.420 --> 00:19:46.430
 far dem, far dem,

00:19:46.430 --> 00:19:48.849
di, di kinder hobn khasene gegat?

00:19:48.973 --> 00:19:51.633
nit,... d- di, di tokhter's?

00:19:51.117 --> 00:19:52.629
di tokhters?

00:19:52.163 --> 00:19:55.660
neyn, nit beyde, zey hobn nokh nit khasene gehat.

00:19:56.027 --> 00:19:57.759
zey hobn nit khasene gehat.

00:19:57.850 --> 00:20:00.160
nor er hot khasene gehat.

00:20:00.330 --> 00:20:01.269
 ver?

00:20:00.651 --> 00:20:02.957
un eyn m-, der man,

00:20:03.216 --> 00:20:04.880
mayn tokhter's man.

00:20:05.055 --> 00:20:06.618
er iz geblibn...

00:20:05.595 --> 00:20:09.010
neyn, nisht, ikh red nisht fun yetst. ikh red fun UNK

00:20:09.010 --> 00:20:13.743
ven ir zent gekumen un gevoynt in BAT YAM, di kinder zenen groys gevorn,

00:20:10.243 --> 00:20:11.720
in BAT YA-...

00:20:13.743 --> 00:20:15.275
khasene gehat...

00:20:13.920 --> 00:20:18.660
y- neyn, hobn nokh nit kh- ge- UNK mayne kinder? ya.

00:20:17.577 --> 00:20:20.450
dayne kinder, yo, dayne tekhters.

00:20:19.070 --> 00:20:21.792
⟨zi, ya,⟩ mayne hobn khasene gehat. ⟨di mey-⟩

00:20:21.792 --> 00:20:23.724
di eltere hot khasene gehat;

00:20:23.724 --> 00:20:27.898
zi iz nit gegangen in armey, vayle zi hot khasene gehat tsu akhtsn yor.

00:20:27.567 --> 00:20:28.286
ya.

00:20:28.240 --> 00:20:31.779
 un er iz geven nayntsn. er iz nokh geven in armey,

00:20:28.478 --> 00:20:29.636
un zi hot...

00:20:31.937 --> 00:20:34.631
nor, zayne eltern

00:20:35.194 --> 00:20:38.259
vos iz di nomen fun ayer tokhter, di groyse?

00:20:35.300 --> 00:20:36.660
hobn...

00:20:38.130 --> 00:20:39.720
di vos iz geshtorbn?

00:20:39.058 --> 00:20:39.980
yo.

00:20:39.720 --> 00:20:40.486
LEYA.

00:20:40.510 --> 00:20:43.187
dertseylt... ⟨L- un LEYA,⟩ un di kleyne...

00:20:42.248 --> 00:20:46.714
LEYA, zi iz geven sheyn vi di velt, un zi iz geven a baleboste,

00:20:46.939 --> 00:20:49.582
un m'hot zey geholfn aynordenen.

00:20:49.858 --> 00:20:52.330
itster arbet er in ⟨EYLAL⟩.

00:20:52.238 --> 00:20:54.493
un zi hot geborn dray kinder?

00:20:54.441 --> 00:20:55.441
ha?

00:20:54.887 --> 00:20:57.159
zi hot geborn dray kinder?

00:20:57.267 --> 00:21:00.799
zi hot geborn dray kinder do. er iz geblibn

00:21:00.799 --> 00:21:02.796
mit a kind fun

00:21:02.852 --> 00:21:06.360
onderhalbn yor, nokh keyn tsvey yor nit, oyfn hant,

00:21:05.687 --> 00:21:07.048
vos iz geshen?

00:21:06.852 --> 00:21:08.246
az zi iz geshtorbn.

00:21:07.915 --> 00:21:10.270
yo. vos iz geshen? ⟨zi⟩...

00:21:09.771 --> 00:21:11.925
bay ir iz geven a pintele,

00:21:11.931 --> 00:21:14.070
un m'hot nit geleygt keyn akht;

00:21:14.074 --> 00:21:15.873
m'hot nit gevust vos.

00:21:16.504 --> 00:21:19.985
nokh hot zi, a- az zi iz shoyn, dernokh iz geven

00:21:19.985 --> 00:21:23.248
di bar-mitsve fun mayn, fun ir zun,

00:21:23.524 --> 00:21:28.590
un nokh di bar-mitsve hot zi do dershpirt epes a gulke untern pakhve.

00:21:28.823 --> 00:21:31.280
un az iz hot shoyn dershpirt di gulke,

00:21:31.843 --> 00:21:34.368
un m'iz avek tsum profesor,

00:21:34.864 --> 00:21:39.910
iz shoyn geven tsu shpet. ot do in dem pintl iz geven bay ir

00:21:39.910 --> 00:21:42.182
a SARTAN MENALOMA,

00:21:42.222 --> 00:21:45.250
un dos iz ir arayn ineveynik,

00:21:45.495 --> 00:21:49.220
un tsayt nayn khadoshim iz zi avekgeshtorbn.

00:21:48.769 --> 00:21:50.771
vi alt iz zi geven demlt?

00:21:50.271 --> 00:21:53.218
az zi iz geshtorbn? fir un draysik yor.

00:21:52.988 --> 00:21:55.050
LEYA. ya.

00:21:54.102 --> 00:21:57.606
hot zi ibergelozn a tsv⟨ik-⟩ a tsvey-yorike kind.

00:21:57.713 --> 00:22:00.560
der yingl iz geven nokh bar-mitsve,

00:22:00.560 --> 00:22:03.748
un di meydele, eyne iz geven elf yor.

00:22:04.395 --> 00:22:09.789
un, iz er hot ge-, iz hot er g- g- g- gegangen zukhn a vayb.

00:22:10.116 --> 00:22:13.890
hot er gefunen a vayb vos zi hot oykh gehat tsvey kinder.

00:22:14.280 --> 00:22:18.260
 un zeyer nit keyn gute far undzere kinder.

00:22:18.385 --> 00:22:21.534
ober di kleyninke hot zi oysgehodevet,

00:22:21.692 --> 00:22:23.930
iz di kleyninke iz gut,

00:22:23.970 --> 00:22:27.780
ober di tsvey kinder iz di gantsinke tsayt,

00:22:27.780 --> 00:22:33.080
hobn mir gedarft zey helfn. oto der man mayner helft zey zeyer a sakh.

00:22:32.863 --> 00:22:36.560
vos iz, vi azoy iz gevezn nokh di...

00:22:36.560 --> 00:22:39.219
in velekhe yor iz dayn tokhter geshtorbn?

00:22:39.394 --> 00:22:43.360
in fir un akhtsik. un nokh mayn tokhter's toyt...

00:22:44.406 --> 00:22:48.787
mayn tokhter iz gelegn in IKHILOV, dortn in onkologye.

00:22:48.338 --> 00:22:49.175
yo.

00:22:49.249 --> 00:22:52.028
hot zi gezogt, "MAMA,

00:22:52.168 --> 00:22:54.671
ikh'l shoyn fun danet nit aroys."

00:22:54.671 --> 00:22:59.587
m'hot ir di le- farn shtarbn hot men ir gebrakht oto do o in onkologye.

00:22:59.307 --> 00:23:00.111
yo.

00:23:00.268 --> 00:23:03.120
zogt zi, "ikh'l shoyn fun danet ⟨nit a-⟩...

00:23:03.120 --> 00:23:04.818
nor eyn zakh vil ikh:

00:23:05.280 --> 00:23:09.260
ikh'l lign in mitn, un du mitn papn bay di zaytn.

00:23:10.343 --> 00:23:13.820
ikh vil mit aykh tsuzamen lign oyf di kvorim."

00:23:14.325 --> 00:23:17.677
hobn mir glaykh gemakht dray matseyves,

00:23:19.287 --> 00:23:23.313
glaykh dray kvorim, un mayn man

00:23:23.826 --> 00:23:30.452
hot gezen di kvorim, un oyfn dritn monat iz mayn man arayn in zayn keyver.

00:23:30.620 --> 00:23:34.277
 vayle er hot dos nit gekent durkhmakhn merer.

00:23:34.277 --> 00:23:37.940
er hot mir in geto, mayn man, eyn zakh gezogt:

00:23:37.940 --> 00:23:41.286
"ikh hob farlorn di gantse mishpokhe, beshas ⟨mir hobn dan...⟩,

00:23:41.511 --> 00:23:47.118
brider un shvester un mame un tate. nor aza veytik vi me farlirt a kind

00:23:47.118 --> 00:23:48.940
iz nito oyf der velt."

00:23:48.940 --> 00:23:52.321
un az er hot farlorn aza sheyne, zise kind,

00:23:52.564 --> 00:23:58.010
iz er arayngegangen punkt oyfn dritn monat, geplatst im an oder in kop,

00:23:58.010 --> 00:24:02.450
un er iz arayn in ir keyver, in keyver lebn mayn tokht⟨er⟩.

00:24:02.450 --> 00:24:05.079
zaynen geblibn di tsvey kinder,

00:24:06.162 --> 00:24:11.154
un azoy vi ikh hob getrofn mayn... der iz geven undzerer a khaver,

00:24:11.481 --> 00:24:15.778
mayn, der man, vos er fleg keseyder kumen tsu undz in shtub,

00:24:15.784 --> 00:24:17.690
az mayn man hot gelebt.

00:24:15.902 --> 00:24:18.590
 eyn, eyn minut. iz geblibn,

00:24:18.590 --> 00:24:22.680
 di, di dray kinder fun dayn tokhter, LEYA,

00:24:22.680 --> 00:24:26.650
un du host gegat nokh eyn tokhter, v- du host nokh eyn tokhter.

00:24:25.593 --> 00:24:27.560
zi iz UNK...

00:24:26.650 --> 00:24:28.029
ir nome⟨r⟩ iz...?

00:24:27.647 --> 00:24:31.290
di tsveyte tokhter hot, hot tsvey kinder.

00:24:28.626 --> 00:24:29.632
ya.

00:24:30.786 --> 00:24:34.307
vos ⟨iz, vi az-⟩, vi azoy ruft zi zikh on, dayn tokhter?

00:24:34.077 --> 00:24:35.978
⟨, zi,⟩ KHANA.

00:24:36.000 --> 00:24:37.040
KHANA.

00:24:36.051 --> 00:24:39.977
di tokh- ire tsvey kinder zaynen adoptirte.

00:24:39.848 --> 00:24:42.137
adoptirte kinder. un...

00:24:41.080 --> 00:24:42.964
vayle zi hot gehat,

00:24:43.223 --> 00:24:46.910
zi hot gehat, nayn mol hot zi gehat

00:24:46.910 --> 00:24:50.203
maplen. zi hot nit gekent oykhet oysshvangern.

00:24:50.530 --> 00:24:54.270
hot zi genumen a yingele un zi hot genumen a meydele.

00:24:54.462 --> 00:24:55.353
NINA,

00:24:55.353 --> 00:24:57.374
nokh dem toyt fun dayn man,

00:24:58.309 --> 00:25:02.620
 vi azoy, vi azoy iz geven dayn le-...

00:25:00.881 --> 00:25:02.670
a bisele hekher.

00:25:02.620 --> 00:25:07.449
vi azoy iz geven dayn lebn, nokh di toyt fun dayn tokhter un dayn man?

00:25:07.710 --> 00:25:10.310
UNK, vi iz geven mayn lebn?

00:25:08.805 --> 00:25:10.959
host geleb- host geARBEIT?

00:25:10.729 --> 00:25:12.740
ikh hob, ⟨vey!⟩

00:25:13.142 --> 00:25:15.397
nokh mayn ⟨d-⟩ nokh zeyer toyt

00:25:15.133 --> 00:25:15.954
neyn?

00:25:15.859 --> 00:25:18.890
bin ikh geven a halb yor bay mayn tokhter.

00:25:19.285 --> 00:25:21.390
kh'hob gehat a sheyne shtub,

00:25:21.394 --> 00:25:24.268
ober ikh hob nit gekent aroyfgeyn in ir.

00:25:24.268 --> 00:25:28.310
mayn eydem flegt mir brengen zakhn zikh ibertsuton,

00:25:28.310 --> 00:25:30.736
un mir iz geven zeyer shlekht.

00:25:31.705 --> 00:25:38.100
ikh fleg nit esn un nit trinken, un ikh bin geven bay mayn tokhter. kh'hob moyre gehat aroyftsugeyn in shtub.

00:25:38.370 --> 00:25:41.370
un der man hot mir vayter geratevet.

00:25:40.969 --> 00:25:42.397
der man...

00:25:41.610 --> 00:25:44.490
er flegt kumen tsu un-...

00:25:43.045 --> 00:25:44.625
vos iz zayn nomen?

00:25:44.490 --> 00:25:46.880
, Dov Grinshteyn.

00:25:46.217 --> 00:25:49.333
Dov Grinshteyn iz dayn man ⟨y-⟩ haynt?

00:25:48.934 --> 00:25:52.606
UNK dos iz geven undzerer a khaver nokh fun geto.

00:25:52.444 --> 00:25:54.648
nokh in, ŠIAULIAI?

00:25:54.520 --> 00:25:58.340
ya. un er iz oykh geven in, in DACHAU,

00:25:54.992 --> 00:25:55.981
ya.

00:25:58.340 --> 00:26:00.606
ober mir hobn im do getrofn,

00:26:00.882 --> 00:26:04.706
az er iz do gekumen in zibn un fertsikstn yor.

00:26:04.830 --> 00:26:08.216
flegn mir zikh khavern. un er hot gehat a vayb,

00:26:08.391 --> 00:26:11.780
un er hot gelebt mit ir do. di ershte vayb

00:26:11.780 --> 00:26:14.825
hot oykh opgefrorn di fis in lager,

00:26:14.825 --> 00:26:19.322
un, m'hot ir aropgenumen di fis un zi iz geshtorbn,

00:26:19.322 --> 00:26:21.810
glaykh fun di bafrayung.

00:26:21.810 --> 00:26:23.510
er hot ir nit gezen.

00:26:23.510 --> 00:26:28.040
hot er do khasene gehat, un er hot gelebt mit di vayb draysik yor,

00:26:28.040 --> 00:26:32.291
un zi iz, ts- tsu zekhtsik yor geshtorbn fun a SARTAN.

00:26:32.291 --> 00:26:34.172
iz er geven aleyn.

00:26:34.172 --> 00:26:36.870
keyn kinder mit di vayb hot er nit gehat.

00:26:36.623 --> 00:26:40.414
un ale yorn gevern, gevezn ayere FREUND?

00:26:40.200 --> 00:26:43.740
ye, di, nit ale yorn. mir zaynen dokh gekumen...

00:26:42.563 --> 00:26:45.540
do in land. do in land. do in land.

00:26:44.284 --> 00:26:50.130
 mir zaynen dokh gekumen do in nayn un, un fuftsik. er iz gekumen ⟨in⟩ zibn un fer-...

00:26:47.680 --> 00:26:51.110
⟨oh,⟩ fun da- ya, ya, fun danet.

00:26:50.207 --> 00:26:54.130
ober er fleg k-, iz dernokh iz zayn vayb geshtorbn.

00:26:54.358 --> 00:26:57.271
flegt er keseyder kumen tsu undz,

00:26:57.413 --> 00:26:59.975
un er flegt helfn di kinder,

00:26:59.975 --> 00:27:03.937
 i- vos m'hot gedarft in shtub; er iz a balebos.

00:27:04.315 --> 00:27:07.140
un er flegt zikh mit undz, er iz geven bay di,

00:27:07.140 --> 00:27:09.650
 tokhter oyf di levaye.

00:27:09.650 --> 00:27:13.280
er hot ayngeordnt, geholfn aynordenen mit di kvorim.

00:27:13.663 --> 00:27:16.458
un, ⟨⟩, oyf mayn man's levaye.

00:27:16.465 --> 00:27:20.981
un dernokh, az ikh bin geblibn aleyn, un er iz geven finf yor aleyn,

00:27:21.139 --> 00:27:25.554
hot er mir, tsugenumen aher. er hot gefregt bay man tokhter,

00:27:26.320 --> 00:27:30.460
tsi iz zi aynshtimik: "ikh vil tsunemen di mamen." v⟨UNK⟩,

00:27:30.460 --> 00:27:32.490
vayle anit volt ikh oykh geshtorbn.

00:27:32.910 --> 00:27:36.580
ikh hob dos nit gekent fun azoy fil iberlebn.

00:27:36.580 --> 00:27:38.340
UNK vos,

00:27:38.340 --> 00:27:41.310
az ikh bin gekumen punkt in a yor arum...

00:27:41.310 --> 00:27:43.500
ikh bin geven bay mayn tokhter UNK...

00:27:43.500 --> 00:27:45.200
az ikh bin gekumen aher

00:27:45.200 --> 00:27:49.145
⟨iz⟩ tsevishn andere mentshn, tsevishn an ander svive,

00:27:49.607 --> 00:27:54.413
un tsevishn alts, hob ikh zikh kam a bisl baruikt.

00:27:54.413 --> 00:27:57.830
vayle m'hot dos nit gekent durkhmakhn.

00:27:57.830 --> 00:27:59.743
ot vet ir zen vi sheyn,

00:28:00.458 --> 00:28:04.097
vi sheyn di tokhter, v⟨UNK⟩ vemen ikh hob farlorn.

00:28:05.267 --> 00:28:08.467
dos, dos iz geven mayn letster,

00:28:08.524 --> 00:28:13.108
m- mayn letster etap, vos ikh, tomer iz shoyn mir oysgekumen tsu lebn...

00:28:13.384 --> 00:28:15.723
un kh'hob gehat azoy fil nakhes.

00:28:15.814 --> 00:28:17.985
kh'fleg arayngeyn tsu ir in shtub.

00:28:18.092 --> 00:28:22.507
der gantser blok, ale, gants RAM-... in R⟨AM⟩AT HANASI hot zi gelebt...

00:28:22.581 --> 00:28:28.042
flegn ale zogn az s'iz nito aza ⟨zoyberantin⟩ un aza baleboste vi zi iz geven:

00:28:28.369 --> 00:28:30.624
ir tish, vi zi fleg dekn,

00:28:30.900 --> 00:28:35.080
ire, vi zi flegt h- ire kinder firn.

00:28:35.153 --> 00:28:37.324
altsding iz geven,

00:28:37.650 --> 00:28:39.652
ober zi iz avekgeshtorbn.

00:28:41.042 --> 00:28:45.052
un dos iz gevezn, iz dernokh bin ikh gekumen aher.

00:28:41.076 --> 00:28:42.150
NINA.

00:28:45.312 --> 00:28:47.803
ober di tsvey groyse kinder,

00:28:47.809 --> 00:28:51.515
di meydl lebt nokh bay dem tatn in shtub in a tsimer,

00:28:51.792 --> 00:28:55.026
ober zi hot afile nit a kap vaser fun ir;

00:28:55.048 --> 00:28:57.860
di shtifmame iz mit ir shreklekh.

00:28:58.238 --> 00:29:00.201
zi hot tsvey tekhter,

00:29:00.201 --> 00:29:03.050
un zey hobn a shutfesdikn kind,

00:29:03.050 --> 00:29:07.380
un undzer meydele iz dortn do. zi iz itster fuftsn yor.

00:29:07.401 --> 00:29:09.790
du bist nont tsu dayne,...

00:29:08.899 --> 00:29:09.899
ha?

00:29:09.790 --> 00:29:10.905
du bist nont,

00:29:10.978 --> 00:29:12.946
 tsu dayne eyniklekh?

00:29:12.733 --> 00:29:16.220
zey- UNK, di groyse helfn mir dokh alts.

00:29:15.872 --> 00:29:16.608
ya.

00:29:16.345 --> 00:29:20.186
mayn man, der helft zeyer a sakh mayne kinder.

00:29:20.344 --> 00:29:24.270
NINA, mir veln yetst endikn dize kasete,

00:29:24.270 --> 00:29:29.689
un m'vet, vayter geyn mit di, mit di fifte kasete.

00:29:29.689 --> 00:29:30.652
TODA RABA.

00:29:29.730 --> 00:29:30.986
⟨ariber-...⟩

00:29:31.077 --> 00:29:33.310
nu, me darf nokh reydn?
